{"tid":1848543,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【1.29抗疫罷工】連信都幫大家準備埋","createTime":"2020-01-28T13:42:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T14:15:35.000Z","uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1ededfc941a8a064b0a5eba9194fca834bfb1e69","tid":1848543,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:42:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">行動！行動！行動！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1 戴白絲帶<br />\n2 周圍share醫護罷工相關文宣<br />\n3 身體力行，一齊罷工<br />\n4 如果得閒，落街擺站派文宣派白絲帶</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n‼️1.29開始 全城抗疫 罷工自保‼️<br />\n<br />\n提供以下兩個範本，如果你去過高危地區或者同過高危人士接觸，呼籲申請「自我隔離」。如果係名正言順罷工，請參考第二個範本！如果有任何需要或者疑問，記得向所屬工會求助！<br />\n<br />\n1️⃣自願向僱主作「健康申報」及自我隔離通知<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1UamgTmt0n-__YEkgzIfEjmXFzq2cgUCcO77EVgI1Tss/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1UamgTmt0n-__YEkgzIfEjmXFzq2cgUCcO77EVgI1Tss%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGbQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=7aa053b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1UamgTmt0n-__YEkgzIfEjmXFzq2cgUCcO77EVgI1Tss/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n2️⃣有關僱員參與抗疫罷工通知<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1ZFBlLpVxQessEMbrphucXv4tL9hsG-vuAInd1MjvDqc/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1ZFBlLpVxQessEMbrphucXv4tL9hsG-vuAInd1MjvDqc%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGbQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=f78f65b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1ZFBlLpVxQessEMbrphucXv4tL9hsG-vuAInd1MjvDqc/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n----<br />\n🔴二百萬三罷聯合陣線🔴<br />\n抗爭 | 工會 | 罷工 | 行業行動<br />\n<br />\n頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGbQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=aa614ac5\" tar